title: Laos national under-23 football team
text:
Laos national under-23 football team (also known as Laos Under-23, Laos U-23 or Laos Olympic Team) represents <a href="Laos">Laos</a> in international <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> competitions in <a href="Olympic%20Games">Olympic Games</a>, <a href="Asian%20Games">Asian Games</a> and <a href="SEA%20Games">SEA Games</a>, as well as any other under-23 international football tournaments.
